這張專輯定名為《夏日傾情》，同時以西班牙文命名為「Apasionese en el Verano」，配合《[[黎明夏日傾情演唱會|黎明夏日傾情演唱會]]》而推出，唱片封套以夏日色彩為設計概念，黎明在封面照展現出閑適、悠然自得的情感<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://i.imgur.com/vrqQ4zB.jpg|title = 黎明難忘那段意粉生涯|date = 1993-07-27|publisher = 新電視1018期|language = zh|accessdate = 2022-01-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220116024954/https://i.imgur.com/vrqQ4zB.jpg |archive-date = 2022-01-16 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。兩首主打歌〈夏日燒着了〉及〈夏日傾情〉曾用作電訊廣告歌曲，〈夏日燒着了〉改編自日本樂團[[南方之星|南方之星]]的作品，曲風以老式的爵士樂為主<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://comebacktolove.blogspot.com/2020/02/1993.html |title = 黎明－夏日傾情（1993）|publisher = 80－90年代廣東歌－come back to love |language = zh |accessdate = 2022-01-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200920083531/http://comebacktolove.blogspot.com/2020/02/1993.html |archive-date = 2022-01-16 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，黎明在音樂短片中演繹的舞蹈由林青峰編排<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://i.imgur.com/pDhUzzz.jpg|title = 人物專訪林青峰|date = 1994-10|publisher = 黎明家族會刊第十四期|language = zh|accessdate = 2022-01-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220116035440/https://i.imgur.com/pDhUzzz.jpg |archive-date = 2022-01-16 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>；〈夏日傾情〉改編自日本歌手[[谷村新司|谷村新司]]的作品，由[[向雪懷|向雪懷]]填詞，內容講述一個少女與情人之間的感情承諾，體現出二人久久不見，盼望在夏日相聚的那份春去秋來感覺<ref name="黃國恩">{{Cite book | author = 黃國恩 | title = 我們的四大天王──九十年代樂壇風光 | location = 香港 | publisher = 非凡出版 | date = 2020-07 | pages = 128－129 |ISBN = 9789888676002 |language = zh}}</ref>，歌詞中呈現浪漫的意象和寫法，使聽眾切入和投入歌曲中<ref>{{Cite book | author =朱耀偉| title =歲月如歌－詞話香港粵語流行曲|location =香港| publisher =三聯書店(香港)有限公司| date =2009-09| pages = 152| ISBN =9789620428807| language =zh}}</ref>，黎明以當時常見的震音唱法演繹歌曲<ref>{{cite news |language = zh | url = https://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/2296108/|title = 黎明自嘲當年《夏日傾情》勁多震音震過貓王 向歌迷致歉兼重錄|publisher = 頭條日報 |date = 2022-01-06 |accessdate = 2022-01-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220106065243/https://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/2296108/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%98%B2%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4-%E5%A4%8F%E6%97%A5%E5%82%BE%E6%83%85-%E5%8B%81%E5%A4%9A%E9%9C%87%E9%9F%B3%E9%9C%87%E9%81%8E%E8%B2%93%E7%8E%8B-%E5%90%91%E6%AD%8C%E8%BF%B7%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89%E5%85%BC%E9%87%8D%E9%8C%84|archive-date = 2022-01-06|dead-url = no }}</ref>，歌曲的音樂短片由[[電視廣播有限公司|電視廣播有限公司]]綜藝科導演唐婉儀執導<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://i.imgur.com/DDjmOBZ.jpg|title = 人物專訪唐婉儀|date = 1996-12|publisher = 黎明家族會刊第二十五期|language = zh|accessdate = 2022-01-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220120051913/https://i.imgur.com/DDjmOBZ.jpg|archive-date = 2022-01-20|dead-url = yes}}</ref>，黎明和[[江希文|江希文]]合作演出，拍攝地點位於山旁的石屋<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://i.imgur.com/VFcRUuF.jpg|title = 夏日傾情 黎明MTV|date = 1993|publisher = 雜誌|language = zh|accessdate = 2022-01-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220113082714/https://i.imgur.com/VFcRUuF.jpg|archive-date = 2022-01-13|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

